lastCommitMessage: feat: enhance localization for seller post feature
- Updated success and failure messages for post publishing to utilize localized strings, improving user feedback in both English and Traditional Chinese.
- Enhanced input field labels and hints for title, content, tags, and images to reflect localized text, ensuring a consistent user experience.
- Added new localization entries for various post-related actions and messages, contributing to a more user-friendly interface for sellers.
These changes improve accessibility and clarity for users when creating and managing posts.
